text: Nicole Oude Luttikhuis (born 26 December 1997) is a Dutch volleyball player. She was in the Netherlands women's national volleyball team. She participated in the 2015 Montreux Volley Masters and 2015 European Games. == References == Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:Dutch volleyball players Category:Sportspeople from Overijssel
